# The shipped templates under backend/word_templates/ and report-templates/
# are de-branded, generic VibeDocs templates (no client branding or PII) and
# ARE meant to be committed. Only ignore template *backups* so stray snapshots
# never sneak in, plus any scratch/dev artifacts.
**/*.pre-*.docx
**/*.pre-*.xlsx
**/*.prev-*.xlsx
**/*.bak
**/*.backup
~$*
docs/_*.py
docs/_*.jpg
